[[test]]
name = "integration"
required-features = [ "testing",]

[package]
authors = [ "Damir Jelić <poljar@termina.org.uk>",]
description = "A high level Matrix client-server library."
edition = "2021"
homepage = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
keywords = [ "matrix", "chat", "messaging", "ruma", "nio",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
name = "matrix-sdk"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
rust-version = "1.82"
version = "0.9.0"

[features]
default = [ "e2e-encryption", "automatic-room-key-forwarding", "sqlite", "native-tls",]
testing = [ "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/testing", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/testing", "matrix-sdk-base/testing", "wiremock", "matrix-sdk-test", "assert_matches2",]
e2e-encryption = [ "matrix-sdk-base/e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/crypto-store", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/e2e-encryption",]
js = [ "matrix-sdk-common/js", "matrix-sdk-base/js",]
sqlite = [ "dep:matrix-sdk-sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/state-store", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/event-cache",]
bundled-sqlite = [ "sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/bundled",]
indexeddb = [ "matrix-sdk-indexeddb/state-store",]
qrcode = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/qrcode",]
automatic-room-key-forwarding = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/automatic-room-key-forwarding",]
markdown = [ "ruma/markdown",]
native-tls = [ "reqwest/native-tls",]
rustls-tls = [ "reqwest/rustls-tls",]
socks = [ "reqwest/socks",]
sso-login = [ "dep:axum", "dep:rand", "dep:tower",]
uniffi = [ "dep:uniffi", "matrix-sdk-base/uniffi", "dep:matrix-sdk-ffi-macros",]
experimental-oidc = [ "ruma/unstable-msc2967", "ruma/unstable-msc4108", "dep:chrono", "dep:language-tags", "dep:mas-oidc-client", "dep:rand", "dep:sha2", "dep:tower", "dep:openidconnect",]
experimental-widgets = [ "dep:language-tags", "dep:uuid",]
docsrs = [ "e2e-encryption", "sqlite", "indexeddb", "sso-login", "qrcode",]

[dependencies]
anymap2 = "0.13.0"
aquamarine = "0.6.0"
as_variant = "1.2.0"
async-channel = "2.3.1"
async-stream = "0.3.5"
async-trait = "0.1.83"
bytes = "1.8.0"
bytesize = "1.3"
event-listener = "5.3.1"
futures-core = "0.3.31"
futures-util = "0.3.31"
growable-bloom-filter = "2.1.1"
http = "1.1.0"
indexmap = "2.6.0"
js_int = "0.2.2"
mime = "0.3.17"
mime2ext = "0.1.53"
once_cell = "1.20.2"
percent-encoding = "2.3.1"
pin-project-lite = "0.2.15"
serde = "1.0.151"
serde_html_form = "0.2.0"
serde_json = "1.0.91"
tempfile = "3.9.0"
thiserror = "2.0.3"
urlencoding = "2.1.3"
zeroize = "1.8.1"

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.93"
assert-json-diff = "2.0.2"
assert_matches = "1.5.0"
assert_matches2 = "0.1.2"
dirs = "5.0.1"
futures-executor = "0.3.21"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
similar-asserts = "1.6.0"
stream_assert = "0.1.1"
tokio-test = "0.4.4"

[dependencies.anyhow]
optional = true
version = "1.0.93"

[dependencies.assert_matches2]
optional = true
version = "0.1.2"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7.9"
optional = true

[dependencies.chrono]
optional = true
version = "0.4.38"

[dependencies.eyeball]
version = "0.8.8"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyeball-im]
version = "0.5.1"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyre]
version = "0.6.12"
optional = true

[dependencies.imbl]
features = [ "serde",]
version = "3.0.0"

[dependencies.language-tags]
version = "0.3.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.mas-oidc-client]
version = "0.11.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.9.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-common]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-common"
version = "0.9.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-ffi-macros]
optional = true
path = "bindings/matrix-sdk-ffi-macros"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-indexeddb]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-indexeddb"
version = "0.9.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-sqlite]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-sqlite"
version = "0.9.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-test]
optional = true
path = "testing/matrix-sdk-test"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.rand]
optional = true
version = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.ruma]
features = [ "rand", "unstable-msc2448", "unstable-msc2965", "unstable-msc3930", "unstable-msc3245-v1-compat", "unstable-msc2867", "unstable-msc4230", "client-api-c", "compat-upload-signatures", "compat-user-id", "compat-arbitrary-length-ids", "compat-tag-info", "compat-encrypted-stickers", "unstable-msc3401", "unstable-msc3266", "unstable-msc3488", "unstable-msc3489", "unstable-msc4075", "unstable-msc4140", "unstable-msc4171",]
git = "https://github.com/ruma/ruma"
rev = "b868438f5d91918e97d2c3f64d7c82a0d86d29d4"

[dependencies.sha2]
optional = true
version = "0.10.8"

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
features = [ "sync",]
version = "0.1.14"

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.5.1"
features = [ "util",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing]
features = [ "attributes", "std",]
version = "0.1.40"
default-features = false

[dependencies.uniffi]
optional = true
version = "0.28.0"

[dependencies.url]
features = [ "serde",]
version = "2.5.4"

[dependencies.uuid]
features = [ "serde", "v4",]
optional = true
version = "1.11.0"

[dependencies.vodozemac]
git = "https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac"
rev = "3d655add09992d17fdb2b55c60f532658090487d"
features = [ "insecure-pk-encryption",]

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
features = [ "testing",]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.9.0"

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-test]
path = "testing/matrix-sdk-test"
version = "0.7.0"

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
features = [ "env-filter",]
version = "0.3.18"

[lints.rust]
rust_2018_idioms = "warn"
semicolon_in_expressions_from_macros = "warn"
unused_extern_crates = "warn"
unused_import_braces = "warn"
unused_qualifications = "warn"
trivial_casts = "warn"
trivial_numeric_casts = "warn"

[lints.clippy]
assigning_clones = "allow"
box_default = "allow"
cloned_instead_of_copied = "warn"
dbg_macro = "warn"
inefficient_to_string = "warn"
macro_use_imports = "warn"
mut_mut = "warn"
needless_borrow = "warn"
nonstandard_macro_braces = "warn"
str_to_string = "warn"
todo = "warn"
unused_async = "warn"
redundant_clone = "warn"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3.33"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
tokio-util = "0.7.12"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies]
wiremock = "0.6.2"

[lints.rust.unexpected_cfgs]
level = "warn"
check-cfg = [ "cfg(tarpaulin_include)", "cfg(ruma_unstable_exhaustive_types)",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.gloo-timers]
features = [ "futures",]
version = "0.3.0"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.reqwest]
features = [ "gzip", "http2",]
version = "0.12.4"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.41.1"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.backoff]
version = "0.4.0"
features = [ "tokio",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.openidconnect]
version = "4.0.0-rc.1"
optional = true

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.reqwest]
features = [ "stream", "gzip", "http2",]
version = "0.12.4"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "fs", "rt", "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.41.1"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.wiremock]
optional = true
version = "0.6.2"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.proptest]
version = "1.5.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "rt-multi-thread", "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.41.1"
default-features = false
